2005年9月，美國嘻哈歌手[[肯伊·威斯特|肯伊·威斯特]]在艾比室錄音棚為其專輯《{{link-en|Late Orchestration|Late Orchestration}}》錄製歌曲。2011年6月，南韓偶像團體[[SHINee|SHINee]]成為第一個在艾比路錄音室表演的亞洲團體<ref>{{Cite news|title=샤이니, 英 애비로드 쇼케이스 성공리 마쳐|language=ko|newspaper=Nate News (SK Communications)|date=2011-06-21|url=http://news.nate.com/view/20110621n03720|accessdate=2021-03-22|archive-date=2021-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210303022926/https://news.nate.com/view/20110621n03720|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2011年11月，澳洲歌手[[凱莉·米洛|凱莉·米洛]]在艾比路錄音室錄製了她的專輯《{{link-en|The Abbey Road Sessions (凱莉·米洛專輯)|The Abbey Road Sessions (Kylie Minogue album)|The Abbey Road Sessions}}》。

2017年2月，[[南安普頓大學|南安普頓大學]]的學生電台{{link-en|Surge Radio|Surge Radio}}發現了一個罕見的曾在艾比路錄音室使用的{{link-en|英國錄音機|British Tape Recorder|BTR-3錄音機}}<ref>{{cite news |url=https://interestingelectronics.com/old/radio_glen_memories/btr3/btr3_redis/btr3_redis.html |title=The Rescue of the Radio Glen / Abbey Road EMI BTR-3 Tape Recording Machine |publisher=Henry Walmsley |date=2017-05-23 |access-date=2017-05-23 |archive-date=2021-01-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210118035454/https://interestingelectronics.com/old/radio_glen_memories/btr3/btr3_redis/btr3_redis.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://surge.soton.ac.uk/history.phtml |title=Surge Radio History |publisher=SURGE (Southampton University's Radio from Glen Eyre) |date=2001-09-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20011219184400/http://surge.soton.ac.uk/history.phtml |access-date=2001-09-06 |archive-date=2001-12-19 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2017年4月，這台機械被捐贈給艾比路錄音室<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.abbeyroad.com/news/a-welcome-return-for-lost-tape-machine-2176 |title=A Welcome Return For Lost Tape Machine |publisher=Abbey Road Studios |date=2017-04-12 |access-date=2017-04-13 |archive-date=2021-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308101217/https://www.abbeyroad.com/news/a-welcome-return-for-lost-tape-machine-2176 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==出售爭議==
2010年2月17日，由於債務增加，有報道稱EMI有意出售艾比路錄音室，且有地產商對此表示興趣，計劃將其改建為高級公寓<ref name="Times AR Sale">{{cite news|url=http://business.timesonline.co.uk/tol/business/industry_sectors/media/article7029140.ece|title=End for Abbey Road? EMI puts Beatles' studios up for sale at £30m|newspaper=The Times Online|access-date=2010-02-19 | location=London | date=2010-02-17 | first1=Chris | last1=Smyth | first2=Helen | last2=Power}}</ref>。有報道稱[[英國國民信託|英國國民信託]]可能購買艾比路錄音室，以保護這座歷史建築<ref>{{cite web|author = TJ|url = http://www.nationaltrust.org.uk/main/w-global/w-news/w-latest_news/w-news-should-national-trust-save-abbey-road-studios.htm|title = Should the National Trust save Abbey Road Studios|publisher = Nationaltrust.org.uk|access-date = 2010-09-19|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100817154306/http://www.nationaltrust.org.uk/main/w-global/w-news/w-latest_news/w-news-should-national-trust-save-abbey-road-studios.htm|archive-date = 2010-08-17|dead-url = no}}</ref>。一個保護艾比路錄音室的活動試圖讓該建築維持其錄音室功能<ref>{{cite web|title=Stop the legendary studios becoming luxury flats|publisher=Save Abbey Road Studios!|date=2010-02-24|url=http://saveabbeyroadstudios.org/archives/date/2010/02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100224000257/http://saveabbeyroadstudios.org/archives/date/2010/02|archive-date=2010-02-24|accessdate=2021-03-22|dead-url=no}}</ref>。 

2010年2月21日，EMI表示計劃保存錄音室，並尋找投資者贊助復興計劃<ref name="EMI AR Sale">{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/england/london/8527095.stm|title=Abbey Road studios 'not for sale,' says EMI|work=BBC News|access-date=2010-02-20|date=2010-02-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100222053226/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/england/london/8527095.stm|archive-date=2010-02-22|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Listed-Ind">{{Cite news |title=Abbey Road studios to be listed by British authorities |date=2010-02-27 |newspaper=The Independent |url=https://www.independent.co.uk/incoming/abbey-road-studios-to-be-listed-by-british-authorities-5525467.html |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140726060358/http://www.independent.co.uk/incoming/abbey-road-studios-to-be-listed-by-british-authorities-1912945.html |archive-date=2014-07-26 |accessdate=2021-03-22 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。英國政府也在同時將艾比路錄音室列入II級登錄建築，以保護其免受重大改動<ref name="Listed-Ind" /><ref>{{Cite web |title=Abbey Road Studios Grade II Listed |date=2010-02-23 |publisher=The National Heritage List for England |id=1393688 |url=http://www.english-heritage.org.uk/about/news/abbey-road-studios-grade-ii/ |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140727044837/http://www.english-heritage.org.uk/about/news/abbey-road-studios-grade-ii/ |archive-date=2014-07-27 |accessdate=2021-03-22 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。同年12月，艾比路的斑馬線被列入國家遺產名單<ref>{{Cite news |title=Beatles 'Abbey Road' crossing given heritage status |date=2010-12-23 |newspaper=The Independent |url=https://www.independent.co.uk/travel/news-and-advice/beatles-abbey-road-crossing-given-heritage-status-2167647.html |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140726064633/http://www.independent.co.uk/travel/news-and-advice/beatles-abbey-road-crossing-given-heritage-status-2167647.html |archive-date=2014-07-26 |accessdate=2021-03-22 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

[[保羅·麥卡特尼|保羅·麥卡特尼]]於2010年2月16日接受BBC《[[新聞之夜|新聞之夜]]》採訪時表示有幾位曾長期和錄音室有關的人士在嘗試挽救艾比路錄音室，但未透露這些人是誰，亦未透露他自己是否是其中一員。他還說「我和披頭四在那裡有很多回憶」「那仍是個很棒的錄音棚。所以有人試圖拯救它們的行為真是太可愛了」<ref>{{cite news | url = https://www.nytimes.com/2010/02/18/arts/music/18arts-MCCARTNEYEXP_BRF.html | title = McCartney Expresses Hopes for Abbey Road | last = Sisario | first = Ben | newspaper = The New York Times | date = 2010-02-18 | access-date = 2010-03-27 | archive-date = 2021-03-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210308160223/https://www.nytimes.com/2010/02/18/arts/music/18arts-MCCARTNEYEXP_BRF.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

==艾比路學院==
艾比路錄音室在2015年3月成立艾比路學院，目的是培育音樂製作和音響工程人才<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.factmag.com/2015/03/19/abbey-road-studios-open-school-of-music-production-and-sound-engineering/|title=Abbey Road Studios opens school of music production and sound engineering|website=factmag.com|access-date=2017-01-25|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108132234/https://www.factmag.com/2015/03/19/abbey-road-studios-open-school-of-music-production-and-sound-engineering/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。除了倫敦之外，艾比路學院還在[[柏林|柏林]]、[[美茵河畔法蘭克福|法蘭克福]]、[[阿姆斯特丹|阿姆斯特丹]]、[[巴黎|巴黎]]、[[墨爾本|墨爾本]]提供教育機會<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/music/2015/mar/19/music-institute-opens-in-beatles-abbey-road-studios|title=Music institute opens in Beatles' Abbey Road Studios|first=Haroon|last=Siddique|date=2015-03-19|work=The Guardian|accessdate=2021-03-22|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308132527/https://www.theguardian.com/music/2015/mar/19/music-institute-opens-in-beatles-abbey-road-studios|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

